This document is the API specification for citygml4j 2.5.0.
citygml4j is a Java class library for facilitating work with the City Geography Markup Language (CityGML).
citygml4j is open source and licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
Official website and more information at: https://github.com/citygml4j
